 <p>The witness of retractionhood is defined using the witnesses for the two retractions.</p>
</mainmatter> <backmatter><contributions/> <context><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25613</anchor> <rss>erct-002J.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Construction</taxon> <addr>erct-002J</addr>  <route>erct-002J.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>30</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Composition of <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Sections and retractions">retractions</link></title> <meta name="source">
  
  
